# Cases

### Create a case

```
POST /cases
```

A case can be created using the following request schema


```json
{
    "case_type": "",
    "notes": [
        {
            "note_type": "string",
            "content": "string"
        },
    ],
    "people": [
        {
            "name": "string",
            "address": "string",
            "phone_number": "string",
            "postcode": "string",
            "email": "string"
        },
    ]
}
```

#### Arguments

##### Case type (required)
Case type can be either "CLA" or "CCQ".

#### Notes

##### Note type
Note type can be one of "User", "Provider", "Operator", or, "Other"

##### Content
A string up to 5000 characters long.

